{"tid":516870,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完戲聽到個細路講左啲野","createTime":"2018-01-01T18:47:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T19:46:23.000Z","uid":85882,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ac7b23688e82ae65906fddfd93c74e5b13f0ee71","tid":516870,"uid":85882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T18:47:09.000Z","msg":"睇完Coco 牛高馬大都學人流左兩滴眼淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去個廁所既時候聽到個睇落仲係讀緊幼稚園既細路同佢老豆講野<br />\n老: 驚唔驚啲骨頭啊仔<br />\n細: 唔驚<br />\n老: 如果爸爸都變左骨頭既你會點<br />\n細: 個個都會變成骨頭架啦有咩驚喎 你同我都會<br />\n跟住個啲聽唔到<br />\n<br />\n點解咁細個就可以看破紅塵咁 而我就因為聯想到屋企人喊到成隻狗咁<br />\n生死教育真係越細開始接觸越好<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> coco 真係好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  </span>"},{"pid":"291f27156303adcce2e4b3b7250c93cfd812acf9","tid":516870,"uid":85882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T18:50:23.000Z","msg":"remember me~"},{"pid":"a6c3cc5e0efd0c29f4e408babd7f2e61f1354a13","tid":516870,"uid":85882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T18:51:37.000Z","msg":"首歌唔算好聽但聽到我流眼淚"},{"pid":"de49ad4042a826b378cd0739d15e2964dc0f6b83","tid":516870,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T19:13:01.000Z","msg":"我記得在中學時，和朋友說過我注定與人類的幸福無緣，對女人不感興趣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結果變左極度鐘意紅顏禍水。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"890b2a4ee3b7d8bbdb4d58c9a8136012ec4d86fd","tid":516870,"uid":41355,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T19:16:21.000Z","msg":"看你老母破紅塵咩，根本咩紅塵、執迷都無經歷過，咪撚再濫用呢隻字。"},{"pid":"2d1a9f5b39322fff2b858f2688ee0874cad548cb","tid":516870,"uid":105462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"890b2a4ee3b7d8bbdb4d58c9a8136012ec4d86fd","tid":516870,"uid":41355,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T19:16:21.000Z","msg":"看你老母破紅塵咩，根本咩紅塵、執迷都無經歷過，咪撚